STATE
v.
Quintel Martinez AUGUSTINE. No. 130A03. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 18, 2005. G. Patrick Murphy, Special Deputy Attorney General, Edward W. Grannis, Jr., District Attorney, for State.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 3rd day of February 2005 by Defendant for Appropriate Relief:

"Motion Denied by order of the Court in conference this the 18th day of August 2005."
